9AOT_define Situation :: ‚ÄπœÑ ‚áí œÜ‚Ä∫ (‚ÄπSituation'(_')‚Ä∫)
10  situations: ‚ÄπSituation(x) ‚â°‚á©d‚á©f A!x & ‚àÄF (x[F] ‚Üí Propositional([F]))‚Ä∫
11
12AOT_theorem "T-sit": ‚ÄπTruthValue(x) ‚Üí Situation(x)‚Ä∫
13proof(rule "‚ÜíI")
14  AOT_assume ‚ÄπTruthValue(x)‚Ä∫
15  AOT_hence ‚Äπ‚àÉp TruthValueOf(x,p)‚Ä∫
16    using "T-value"[THEN "‚â°‚á©d‚á©fE"] by blast
17  then AOT_obtain p where ‚ÄπTruthValueOf(x,p)‚Ä∫ using "‚àÉE"[rotated] by blast
18  AOT_hence Œ∏: ‚ÄπA!x & ‚àÄF (x[F] ‚â° ‚àÉq((q ‚â° p) & F = [Œªy q]))‚Ä∫
19    using "tv-p"[THEN "‚â°‚á©d‚á©fE"] by blast
20  AOT_show ‚ÄπSituation(x)‚Ä∫
21  proof(rule situations[THEN "‚â°‚á©d‚á©fI"]; safe intro!: "&I" GEN "‚ÜíI" Œ∏[THEN "&E"(1)])
22    fix F
23    AOT_assume ‚Äπx[F]‚Ä∫
24    AOT_hence ‚Äπ‚àÉq((q ‚â° p) & F = [Œªy q])‚Ä∫
25      using Œ∏[THEN "&E"(2), THEN "‚àÄE"(2)[where Œ≤=F], THEN "‚â°E"(1)] by argo
26    then AOT_obtain q where ‚Äπ(q ‚â° p) & F = [Œªy q]‚Ä∫ using "‚àÉE"[rotated] by blast
27    AOT_hence ‚Äπ‚àÉp F = [Œªy p]‚Ä∫ using "&E"(2) "‚àÉI"(2) by metis
28    AOT_thus ‚ÄπPropositional([F])‚Ä∫
29      by (metis "‚â°‚á©d‚á©fI" "prop-prop1")
30  qed
31qed
32
33AOT_theorem "possit-sit:1": ‚ÄπSituation(x) ‚â° ‚ñ°Situation(x)‚Ä∫
34proof(rule "‚â°I"; rule "‚ÜíI")
35  AOT_assume ‚ÄπSituation(x)‚Ä∫
36  AOT_hence 0: ‚ÄπA!x & ‚àÄF (x[F] ‚Üí Propositional([F]))‚Ä∫
37    using situations[THEN "‚â°‚á©d‚á©fE"] by blast
38  AOT_have 1: ‚Äπ‚ñ°(A!x & ‚àÄF (x[F] ‚Üí Propositional([F])))‚Ä∫
39  proof(rule "KBasic:3"[THEN "‚â°E"(2)]; rule "&I")
40    AOT_show ‚Äπ‚ñ°A!x‚Ä∫ using 0[THEN "&E"(1)] by (metis "oa-facts:2"[THEN "‚ÜíE"])
41  next
42    AOT_have ‚Äπ‚àÄF (x[F] ‚Üí Propositional([F])) ‚Üí ‚ñ°‚àÄF (x[F] ‚Üí Propositional([F]))‚Ä∫
43      by (AOT_subst ‚ÄπŒª Œ† . ¬´Propositional([Œ†])¬ª‚Ä∫ ‚ÄπŒª Œ† . ¬´‚àÉp (Œ† = [Œªy p])¬ª‚Ä∫)
44         (auto simp: "prop-prop1" "‚â°Df" "enc-prop-nec:2")
45    AOT_thus ‚Äπ‚ñ°‚àÄF (x[F] ‚Üí Propositional([F]))‚Ä∫
46      using 0[THEN "&E"(2)] "‚ÜíE" by blast
47  qed
48  AOT_show ‚Äπ‚ñ°Situation(x)‚Ä∫
49    by (AOT_subst ‚Äπ¬´Situation(x)¬ª‚Ä∫ ‚Äπ¬´A!x & ‚àÄF (x[F] ‚Üí Propositional([F]))¬ª‚Ä∫)
50       (auto simp: 1 "‚â°Df" situations)
51next
52  AOT_show ‚ÄπSituation(x)‚Ä∫ if ‚Äπ‚ñ°Situation(x)‚Ä∫
53    using "qml:2"[axiom_inst, THEN "‚ÜíE", OF that].
54qed

56AOT_theorem "possit-sit:2": ‚Äπ‚óáSituation(x) ‚â° Situation(x)‚Ä∫
57  using "possit-sit:1"
58  by (metis "RE‚óá" "S5Basic:2" "‚â°E"(1) "‚â°E"(5) "Commutativity of ‚â°")
59
60AOT_theorem "possit-sit:3": ‚Äπ‚óáSituation(x) ‚â° ‚ñ°Situation(x)‚Ä∫
61  using "possit-sit:1" "possit-sit:2" by (meson "‚â°E"(5))
62
63AOT_theorem "possit-sit:4": ‚Äπ‚ùôùíúSituation(x) ‚â° Situation(x)‚Ä∫
64  by (meson "Act-Basic:5" "Act-Sub:2" "RA[2]" "‚â°E"(1) "‚â°E"(6) "possit-sit:2")

67AOT_register_rigid_restricted_type
68  Situation: ‚ÄπSituation(Œ∫)‚Ä∫
69proof
70  AOT_modally_strict {
71    fix p
72    AOT_obtain x where ‚ÄπTruthValueOf(x,p)‚Ä∫ by (metis "instantiation" "p-has-!tv:1")
73    AOT_hence ‚Äπ‚àÉp TruthValueOf(x,p)‚Ä∫ by (rule "‚àÉI")
74    AOT_hence ‚ÄπTruthValue(x)‚Ä∫ by (metis "‚â°‚á©d‚á©fI" "T-value")
75    AOT_hence ‚ÄπSituation(x)‚Ä∫ using "T-sit"[THEN "‚ÜíE"] by blast
76    AOT_thus ‚Äπ‚àÉx Situation(x)‚Ä∫ by (rule "‚àÉI")
77  }
78next
79  AOT_modally_strict {
80    AOT_show ‚ÄπSituation(Œ∫) ‚Üí Œ∫‚Üì‚Ä∫ for Œ∫
81    proof (rule "‚ÜíI")
82      AOT_assume ‚ÄπSituation(Œ∫)‚Ä∫
83      AOT_hence ‚ÄπA!Œ∫‚Ä∫ by (metis "‚â°‚á©d‚á©fE" "&E"(1) situations)
84      AOT_thus ‚ÄπŒ∫‚Üì‚Ä∫ by (metis "russell-axiom[exe,1].œà_denotes_asm")
85    qed
86  }
87next
88  AOT_modally_strict {
89    fix Œ±
90    AOT_show ‚Äπ‚ñ°(Situation(Œ±) ‚Üí ‚ñ°Situation(Œ±))‚Ä∫
91      using "possit-sit:1"[THEN "conventions:3"[THEN "‚â°‚á©d‚á©fE"], THEN "&E"(1), THEN RN]
92      by blast
93  }
94qed

99AOT_define TruthInSituation :: ‚ÄπœÑ ‚áí œÜ ‚áí œÜ‚Ä∫ ("(_ ‚ä®/ _)" [100, 40] 100)
100  "true-in-s": ‚Äπs ‚ä® p ‚â°‚á©d‚á©f s‚ùôŒ£p‚Ä∫
101
102notepad
103begin
104  (* Verify precedence. *)
105  fix x p q
106  have ‚Äπ¬´x ‚ä® p ‚Üí q¬ª = ¬´(x ‚ä® p) ‚Üí q¬ª‚Ä∫
107    by simp
108  have ‚Äπ¬´x ‚ä® p & q¬ª = ¬´(x ‚ä® p) & q¬ª‚Ä∫
109    by simp
110  have ‚Äπ¬´x ‚ä® ¬¨p¬ª = ¬´x ‚ä® (¬¨p)¬ª‚Ä∫
111    by simp
112  have ‚Äπ¬´x ‚ä® ‚ñ°p¬ª = ¬´x ‚ä® (‚ñ°p)¬ª‚Ä∫
113    by simp
114  have ‚Äπ¬´x ‚ä® ‚ùôùíúp¬ª = ¬´x ‚ä® (‚ùôùíúp)¬ª‚Ä∫
115    by simp
116  have ‚Äπ¬´‚ñ°x ‚ä® p¬ª = ¬´‚ñ°(x ‚ä® p)¬ª‚Ä∫
117    by simp
118  have ‚Äπ¬´¬¨x ‚ä® p¬ª = ¬´¬¨(x ‚ä® p)¬ª‚Ä∫
119    by simp
120end
121

123AOT_theorem lem1: ‚ÄπSituation(x) ‚Üí (x ‚ä® p ‚â° x[Œªy p])‚Ä∫
124proof (rule "‚ÜíI"; rule "‚â°I"; rule "‚ÜíI")
125  AOT_assume ‚ÄπSituation(x)‚Ä∫
126  AOT_assume ‚Äπx ‚ä® p‚Ä∫
127  AOT_hence ‚Äπx‚ùôŒ£p‚Ä∫
128    using "true-in-s"[THEN "‚â°‚á©d‚á©fE"] "&E" by blast
129  AOT_thus ‚Äπx[Œªy p]‚Ä∫ using "prop-enc"[THEN "‚â°‚á©d‚á©fE"] "&E" by blast
130next
131  AOT_assume 1: ‚ÄπSituation(x)‚Ä∫
132  AOT_assume ‚Äπx[Œªy p]‚Ä∫
133  AOT_hence ‚Äπx‚ùôŒ£p‚Ä∫
134    using "prop-enc"[THEN "‚â°‚á©d‚á©fI", OF "&I", OF "cqt:2[const_var]"[axiom_inst]] by blast
135  AOT_thus ‚Äπx ‚ä® p‚Ä∫
136    using "true-in-s"[THEN "‚â°‚á©d‚á©fI"] 1 "&I" by blast
137qed

139AOT_theorem "lem2:1": ‚Äπs ‚ä® p ‚â° ‚ñ°s ‚ä® p‚Ä∫
140proof -
141  AOT_have sit: ‚ÄπSituation(s)‚Ä∫
142    by (simp add: Situation.œà)
143  AOT_have ‚Äπs ‚ä® p ‚â° s[Œªy p]‚Ä∫
144    using lem1[THEN "‚ÜíE", OF sit] by blast
145  also AOT_have ‚Äπ‚Ä¶ ‚â° ‚ñ°s[Œªy p]‚Ä∫
146    by (rule "en-eq:2[1]"[unvarify F]) "cqt:2[lambda]"
147  also AOT_have ‚Äπ‚Ä¶ ‚â° ‚ñ°s ‚ä® p‚Ä∫
148    using lem1[THEN RM, THEN "‚ÜíE", OF "possit-sit:1"[THEN "‚â°E"(1), OF sit]]
149    by (metis "KBasic:6" "‚â°E"(2) "Commutativity of ‚â°" "vdash-properties:10")
150  finally show ?thesis.
151qed
152
153AOT_theorem "lem2:2": ‚Äπ‚óás ‚ä® p ‚â° s ‚ä® p‚Ä∫
154proof -
155  AOT_have ‚Äπ‚ñ°(s ‚ä® p ‚Üí ‚ñ°s ‚ä® p)‚Ä∫
156    using "possit-sit:1"[THEN "‚â°E"(1), OF Situation.œà] "lem2:1"[THEN "conventions:3"[THEN "‚â°‚á©d‚á©fE", THEN "&E"(1)]] RM[OF "‚ÜíI", THEN "‚ÜíE"] by blast
157  thus ?thesis by (metis "B‚óá" "S5Basic:13" "T‚óá" "‚â°I" "‚â°E"(1) "vdash-properties:10")
158qed
159
160AOT_theorem "lem2:3": ‚Äπ‚óás ‚ä® p ‚â° ‚ñ°s ‚ä® p‚Ä∫
161  using "lem2:1" "lem2:2" by (metis "‚â°E"(5))
162
163AOT_theorem "lem2:4": ‚Äπ‚ùôùíú(s ‚ä® p) ‚â° s ‚ä® p‚Ä∫
164proof -
165  AOT_have ‚Äπ‚ñ°(s ‚ä® p ‚Üí ‚ñ°s ‚ä® p)‚Ä∫
166    using "possit-sit:1"[THEN "‚â°E"(1), OF Situation.œà]
167      "lem2:1"[THEN "conventions:3"[THEN "‚â°‚á©d‚á©fE", THEN "&E"(1)]] RM[OF "‚ÜíI", THEN "‚ÜíE"] by blast
168  thus ?thesis
169    using "sc-eq-fur:2"[THEN "‚ÜíE"] by blast
170qed

172AOT_theorem "lem2:5": ‚Äπ¬¨s ‚ä® p ‚â° ‚ñ°¬¨s ‚ä® p‚Ä∫
173  by (metis "KBasic2:1" "contraposition:1[2]" "deduction-theorem" "‚â°I" "‚â°E"(3) "‚â°E"(4) "lem2:2")

175AOT_theorem "sit-identity": ‚Äπs = s' ‚â° ‚àÄp(s ‚ä® p ‚â° s' ‚ä® p)‚Ä∫
176proof(rule "‚â°I"; rule "‚ÜíI")
177  AOT_assume ‚Äπs = s'‚Ä∫
178  moreover AOT_have ‚Äπ‚àÄp(s ‚ä® p ‚â° s ‚ä® p)‚Ä∫
179    by (simp add: "oth-class-taut:3:a" "universal-cor")
180  ultimately AOT_show ‚Äπ‚àÄp(s ‚ä® p ‚â° s' ‚ä® p)‚Ä∫
181    using "rule=E" by fast
182next
183  AOT_assume a: ‚Äπ‚àÄp (s ‚ä® p ‚â° s' ‚ä® p)‚Ä∫
184  AOT_show ‚Äπs = s'‚Ä∫
185  proof(safe intro!: "ab-obey:1"[THEN "‚ÜíE", THEN "‚ÜíE"] "&I" GEN "‚â°I" "‚ÜíI")
186    AOT_show ‚ÄπA!s‚Ä∫ using Situation.œà "‚â°‚á©d‚á©fE" "&E"(1) situations by blast
187  next
188    AOT_show ‚ÄπA!s'‚Ä∫ using Situation.œà "‚â°‚á©d‚á©fE" "&E"(1) situations by blast
189  next
190    fix F
191    AOT_assume 0: ‚Äπs[F]‚Ä∫
192    AOT_hence ‚Äπ‚àÉp (F = [Œªy p])‚Ä∫
193      using Situation.œà[THEN situations[THEN "‚â°‚á©d‚á©fE"], THEN "&E"(2), THEN "‚àÄE"(2)[where Œ≤=F], THEN "‚ÜíE"]
194            "prop-prop1"[THEN "‚â°‚á©d‚á©fE"] by blast
195    then AOT_obtain p where F_def: ‚ÄπF = [Œªy p]‚Ä∫
196      using "‚àÉE" by metis
197    AOT_hence ‚Äπs[Œªy p]‚Ä∫ using 0 "rule=E" by blast
198    AOT_hence ‚Äπs ‚ä® p‚Ä∫ using lem1[THEN "‚ÜíE", OF Situation.œà, THEN "‚â°E"(2)] by blast
199    AOT_hence ‚Äπs' ‚ä® p‚Ä∫ using a[THEN "‚àÄE"(2)[where Œ≤=p], THEN "‚â°E"(1)] by blast
200    AOT_hence ‚Äπs'[Œªy p]‚Ä∫ using lem1[THEN "‚ÜíE", OF Situation.œà, THEN "‚â°E"(1)] by blast
201    AOT_thus ‚Äπs'[F]‚Ä∫ using F_def[symmetric] "rule=E" by blast
202  next
203    fix F
204    AOT_assume 0: ‚Äπs'[F]‚Ä∫
205    AOT_hence ‚Äπ‚àÉp (F = [Œªy p])‚Ä∫
206      using Situation.œà[THEN situations[THEN "‚â°‚á©d‚á©fE"], THEN "&E"(2), THEN "‚àÄE"(2)[where Œ≤=F], THEN "‚ÜíE"]
207            "prop-prop1"[THEN "‚â°‚á©d‚á©fE"] by blast
208    then AOT_obtain p where F_def: ‚ÄπF = [Œªy p]‚Ä∫
209      using "‚àÉE" by metis
210    AOT_hence ‚Äπs'[Œªy p]‚Ä∫ using 0 "rule=E" by blast
211    AOT_hence ‚Äπs' ‚ä® p‚Ä∫ using lem1[THEN "‚ÜíE", OF Situation.œà, THEN "‚â°E"(2)] by blast
212    AOT_hence ‚Äπs ‚ä® p‚Ä∫ using a[THEN "‚àÄE"(2)[where Œ≤=p], THEN "‚â°E"(2)] by blast
213    AOT_hence ‚Äπs[Œªy p]‚Ä∫ using lem1[THEN "‚ÜíE", OF Situation.œà, THEN "‚â°E"(1)] by blast
214    AOT_thus ‚Äπs[F]‚Ä∫ using F_def[symmetric] "rule=E" by blast
215  qed
216qed

218AOT_define PartOfSituation :: ‚ÄπœÑ ‚áí œÑ ‚áí œÜ‚Ä∫ (infixl ‚Äπ‚ä¥‚Ä∫ 80)
219  "sit-part-whole": ‚Äπs ‚ä¥ s' ‚â°‚á©d‚á©f ‚àÄp (s ‚ä® p ‚Üí s' ‚ä® p)‚Ä∫
220
221AOT_theorem "part:1": ‚Äπs ‚ä¥ s‚Ä∫
222  by (rule "sit-part-whole"[THEN "‚â°‚á©d‚á©fI"])
223     (safe intro!: "&I" Situation.œà GEN "‚ÜíI")
224
225AOT_theorem "part:2": ‚Äπs ‚ä¥ s' & s ‚â† s' ‚Üí ¬¨(s' ‚ä¥ s)‚Ä∫
226proof(rule "‚ÜíI"; frule "&E"(1); drule "&E"(2); rule "raa-cor:2")
227  AOT_assume 0: ‚Äπs ‚ä¥ s'‚Ä∫
228  AOT_hence a: ‚Äπs ‚ä® p ‚Üí s' ‚ä® p‚Ä∫ for p using "‚àÄE"(2) "sit-part-whole"[THEN "‚â°‚á©d‚á©fE"] "&E" by blast
229  AOT_assume ‚Äπs' ‚ä¥ s‚Ä∫
230  AOT_hence b: ‚Äπs' ‚ä® p ‚Üí s ‚ä® p‚Ä∫ for p using "‚àÄE"(2) "sit-part-whole"[THEN "‚â°‚á©d‚á©fE"] "&E" by blast
231  AOT_have ‚Äπ‚àÄp (s ‚ä® p ‚â° s' ‚ä® p)‚Ä∫ using a b by (simp add: "‚â°I" "universal-cor")
232  AOT_hence 1: ‚Äπs = s'‚Ä∫ using "sit-identity"[THEN "‚â°E"(2)] by metis
233  AOT_assume ‚Äπs ‚â† s'‚Ä∫
234  AOT_hence ‚Äπ¬¨(s = s')‚Ä∫ by (metis "‚â°‚á©d‚á©fE" "=-infix")
235  AOT_thus ‚Äπs = s' & ¬¨(s = s')‚Ä∫ using 1 "&I" by blast
236qed
237
238AOT_theorem "part:3": ‚Äπs ‚ä¥ s' & s' ‚ä¥ s'' ‚Üí s ‚ä¥ s''‚Ä∫
239proof(rule "‚ÜíI"; frule "&E"(1); drule "&E"(2); safe intro!: "&I" GEN "‚ÜíI" "sit-part-whole"[THEN "‚â°‚á©d‚á©fI"] Situation.œà)
240  fix p
241  AOT_assume ‚Äπs ‚ä® p‚Ä∫
242  moreover AOT_assume ‚Äπs ‚ä¥ s'‚Ä∫
243  ultimately AOT_have ‚Äπs' ‚ä® p‚Ä∫
244    using "sit-part-whole"[THEN "‚â°‚á©d‚á©fE", THEN "&E"(2), THEN "‚àÄE"(2)[where Œ≤=p], THEN "‚ÜíE"] by blast
245  moreover AOT_assume ‚Äπs' ‚ä¥ s''‚Ä∫
246  ultimately AOT_show ‚Äπs'' ‚ä® p‚Ä∫
247    using "sit-part-whole"[THEN "‚â°‚á©d‚á©fE", THEN "&E"(2), THEN "‚àÄE"(2)[where Œ≤=p], THEN "‚ÜíE"] by blast
248qed

250AOT_theorem "sit-identity2:1": ‚Äπs = s' ‚â° s ‚ä¥ s' & s' ‚ä¥ s‚Ä∫
251proof (safe intro!: "‚â°I" "&I" "‚ÜíI")
252  AOT_show ‚Äπs ‚ä¥ s'‚Ä∫ if ‚Äπs = s'‚Ä∫
253    using "rule=E" "part:1" that by blast
254next
255  AOT_show ‚Äπs' ‚ä¥ s‚Ä∫ if ‚Äπs = s'‚Ä∫
256    using "rule=E" "part:1" that[symmetric] by blast
257next
258  AOT_assume ‚Äπs ‚ä¥ s' & s' ‚ä¥ s‚Ä∫
259  AOT_thus ‚Äπs = s'‚Ä∫ using "part:2"[THEN "‚ÜíE", OF "&I"]
260    by (metis "‚â°‚á©d‚á©fI" "&E"(1) "&E"(2) "=-infix" "raa-cor:3")
261qed
262
263AOT_theorem "sit-identity2:2": ‚Äπs = s' ‚â° ‚àÄs'' (s'' ‚ä¥ s ‚â° s'' ‚ä¥ s')‚Ä∫
264proof(safe intro!: "‚â°I" "‚ÜíI" Situation.GEN "sit-identity"[THEN "‚â°E"(2)] GEN[where 'a=ùóà])
265  AOT_show ‚Äπs'' ‚ä¥ s'‚Ä∫ if ‚Äπs'' ‚ä¥ s‚Ä∫ and ‚Äπs = s'‚Ä∫ for s''
266    using "rule=E" that by blast
267next
268  AOT_show ‚Äπs'' ‚ä¥ s‚Ä∫ if ‚Äπs'' ‚ä¥ s'‚Ä∫ and ‚Äπs = s'‚Ä∫ for s''
269    using "rule=E" id_sym that by blast
270next
271  AOT_show ‚Äπs' ‚ä® p‚Ä∫ if ‚Äπs ‚ä® p‚Ä∫ and ‚Äπ‚àÄs'' (s'' ‚ä¥ s ‚â° s'' ‚ä¥ s')‚Ä∫ for p
272    using "sit-part-whole"[THEN "‚â°‚á©d‚á©fE", THEN "&E"(2), OF that(2)[THEN "Situation.‚àÄE", THEN "‚â°E"(1), OF "part:1"], THEN "‚àÄE"(2), THEN "‚ÜíE", OF that(1)].
273next
274  AOT_show ‚Äπs ‚ä® p‚Ä∫ if ‚Äπs' ‚ä® p‚Ä∫ and ‚Äπ‚àÄs'' (s'' ‚ä¥ s ‚â° s'' ‚ä¥ s')‚Ä∫ for p
275    using "sit-part-whole"[THEN "‚â°‚á©d‚á©fE", THEN "&E"(2), OF that(2)[THEN "Situation.‚àÄE",
276          THEN "‚â°E"(2), OF "part:1"], THEN "‚àÄE"(2), THEN "‚ÜíE", OF that(1)].
277qed

279AOT_define Persistent :: ‚ÄπœÜ ‚áí œÜ‚Ä∫ (‚ÄπPersistent'(_')‚Ä∫)
280  persistent: ‚ÄπPersistent(p) ‚â°‚á©d‚á©f ‚àÄs (s ‚ä® p ‚Üí ‚àÄs' (s ‚ä¥ s' ‚Üí s' ‚ä® p))‚Ä∫

282AOT_theorem "pers-prop": ‚Äπ‚àÄp Persistent(p)‚Ä∫

292AOT_theorem "thm-null-trivial:1": ‚Äπ‚àÉ!x NullSituation(x)‚Ä∫
293proof (AOT_subst ‚ÄπŒª Œ∫ . ¬´NullSituation(Œ∫)¬ª‚Ä∫ ‚ÄπŒª Œ∫ . ¬´A!Œ∫ & ‚àÄF (Œ∫[F] ‚â° F ‚â† F)¬ª‚Ä∫)
294  AOT_modally_strict {
295    AOT_show ‚ÄπNullSituation(x) ‚â° A!x & ‚àÄF (x[F] ‚â° F ‚â† F)‚Ä∫ for x
296    proof (safe intro!: "‚â°I" "‚ÜíI" "df-null-trivial:1"[THEN "‚â°‚á©d‚á©fI"] dest!: "df-null-trivial:1"[THEN "‚â°‚á©d‚á©fE"])
297      AOT_assume 0: ‚ÄπSituation(x) & ¬¨‚àÉp x ‚ä® p‚Ä∫
298      AOT_have 1: ‚ÄπA!x‚Ä∫ using 0[THEN "&E"(1), THEN situations[THEN "‚â°‚á©d‚á©fE"], THEN "&E"(1)].
299      AOT_have 2: ‚Äπx[F] ‚Üí ‚àÉp F = [Œªy p]‚Ä∫ for F
300        using 0[THEN "&E"(1), THEN situations[THEN "‚â°‚á©d‚á©fE"], THEN "&E"(2), THEN "‚àÄE"(2)]
301        by (metis "‚â°‚á©d‚á©fE" "deduction-theorem" "prop-prop1" "‚ÜíE")
302      AOT_show ‚ÄπA!x & ‚àÄF (x[F] ‚â° F ‚â† F)‚Ä∫
303      proof (safe intro!: "&I" 1 GEN "‚â°I" "‚ÜíI")
304        fix F
305        AOT_assume ‚Äπx[F]‚Ä∫
306        moreover AOT_obtain p where ‚ÄπF = [Œªy p]‚Ä∫
307          using calculation 2[THEN "‚ÜíE"] "‚àÉE"[rotated] by blast
308        ultimately AOT_have ‚Äπx[Œªy p]‚Ä∫ by (metis "rule=E")
309        AOT_hence ‚Äπx ‚ä® p‚Ä∫ using lem1[THEN "‚ÜíE", OF 0[THEN "&E"(1)], THEN "‚â°E"(2)] by blast
310        AOT_hence ‚Äπ‚àÉp (x ‚ä® p)‚Ä∫ by (rule "‚àÉI")
311        AOT_thus ‚ÄπF ‚â† F‚Ä∫ using 0[THEN "&E"(2)] "raa-cor:1" "&I" by blast
312      next
313        fix F :: ‚Äπ<Œ∫> AOT_var‚Ä∫
314        AOT_assume ‚ÄπF ‚â† F‚Ä∫
315        AOT_hence ‚Äπ¬¨(F = F)‚Ä∫ by (metis "‚â°‚á©d‚á©fE" "=-infix")
316        moreover AOT_have ‚ÄπF = F‚Ä∫
317          by (simp add: "id-eq:1")
318        ultimately AOT_show ‚Äπx[F]‚Ä∫ using "&I" "raa-cor:1" by blast
319      qed
320    next
321      AOT_assume 0: ‚ÄπA!x & ‚àÄF (x[F] ‚â° F ‚â† F)‚Ä∫
322      AOT_hence ‚Äπx[F] ‚â° F ‚â† F‚Ä∫ for F using "‚àÄE" "&E" by blast
323      AOT_hence 1: ‚Äπ¬¨x[F]‚Ä∫ for F
324        using "‚â°‚á©d‚á©fE" "id-eq:1" "=-infix" "reductio-aa:1" "‚â°E"(1) by blast
325      AOT_show ‚ÄπSituation(x) & ¬¨‚àÉp x ‚ä® p‚Ä∫
326      proof (safe intro!: "&I" situations[THEN "‚â°‚á©d‚á©fI"] 0[THEN "&E"(1)] GEN "‚ÜíI")
327        AOT_show ‚ÄπPropositional([F])‚Ä∫ if ‚Äπx[F]‚Ä∫ for F using that 1 "&I" "raa-cor:1" by fast
328      next
329        AOT_show ‚Äπ¬¨‚àÉp x ‚ä® p‚Ä∫
330        proof(rule "raa-cor:2")
331          AOT_assume ‚Äπ‚àÉp x ‚ä® p‚Ä∫
332          then AOT_obtain p where ‚Äπx ‚ä® p‚Ä∫ using "‚àÉE"[rotated] by blast
333          AOT_hence ‚Äπx[Œªy p]‚Ä∫
334            using "‚â°‚á©d‚á©fE" "&E"(1) "‚â°E"(1) lem1 "modus-tollens:1" "raa-cor:3" "true-in-s" by fast
335          moreover AOT_have ‚Äπ¬¨x[Œªy p]‚Ä∫
336            by (rule 1[unvarify F]) "cqt:2[lambda]"
337          ultimately AOT_show ‚Äπp & ¬¨p‚Ä∫ for p using "&I" "raa-cor:1" by blast
338        qed
339      qed
340    qed
341  }
342next
343  AOT_show ‚Äπ‚àÉ!x ([A!]x & ‚àÄF (x[F] ‚â° F ‚â† F))‚Ä∫
344    by (simp add: "A-objects!")
345qed

348AOT_theorem "thm-null-trivial:2": ‚Äπ‚àÉ!x TrivialSituation(x)‚Ä∫
349proof (AOT_subst ‚ÄπŒª Œ∫ . ¬´TrivialSituation(Œ∫)¬ª‚Ä∫ ‚ÄπŒª Œ∫ . ¬´A!Œ∫ & ‚àÄF (Œ∫[F] ‚â° ‚àÉp F = [Œªy p])¬ª‚Ä∫)
350  AOT_modally_strict {
351    AOT_show ‚ÄπTrivialSituation(x) ‚â° A!x & ‚àÄF (x[F] ‚â° ‚àÉp F = [Œªy p])‚Ä∫ for x
352    proof (safe intro!: "‚â°I" "‚ÜíI" "df-null-trivial:2"[THEN "‚â°‚á©d‚á©fI"] dest!: "df-null-trivial:2"[THEN "‚â°‚á©d‚á©fE"])
353      AOT_assume 0: ‚ÄπSituation(x) & ‚àÄp x ‚ä® p‚Ä∫
354      AOT_have 1: ‚ÄπA!x‚Ä∫ using 0[THEN "&E"(1), THEN situations[THEN "‚â°‚á©d‚á©fE"], THEN "&E"(1)].
355      AOT_have 2: ‚Äπx[F] ‚Üí ‚àÉp F = [Œªy p]‚Ä∫ for F
356        using 0[THEN "&E"(1), THEN situations[THEN "‚â°‚á©d‚á©fE"], THEN "&E"(2), THEN "‚àÄE"(2)]
357        by (metis "‚â°‚á©d‚á©fE" "deduction-theorem" "prop-prop1" "‚ÜíE")
358      AOT_show ‚ÄπA!x & ‚àÄF (x[F] ‚â° ‚àÉp F = [Œªy p])‚Ä∫
359      proof (safe intro!: "&I" 1 GEN "‚â°I" "‚ÜíI" 2)
360        fix F
361        AOT_assume ‚Äπ‚àÉp F = [Œªy p]‚Ä∫
362        then AOT_obtain p where ‚ÄπF = [Œªy p]‚Ä∫ using "‚àÉE"[rotated] by blast
363        moreover AOT_have ‚Äπx ‚ä® p‚Ä∫ using 0[THEN "&E"(2)] "‚àÄE" by blast
364        ultimately AOT_show ‚Äπx[F]‚Ä∫
365          by (metis 0 "rule=E" "&E"(1) id_sym "‚â°E"(2) lem1 "Commutativity of ‚â°" "‚ÜíE")
366      qed
367    next
368      AOT_assume 0: ‚ÄπA!x & ‚àÄF (x[F] ‚â° ‚àÉp F = [Œªy p])‚Ä∫
369      AOT_hence 1: ‚Äπx[F] ‚â° ‚àÉp F = [Œªy p]‚Ä∫ for F using "‚àÄE" "&E" by blast
370      AOT_have 2: ‚ÄπSituation(x)‚Ä∫
371      proof (safe intro!: "&I" situations[THEN "‚â°‚á©d‚á©fI"] 0[THEN "&E"(1)] GEN "‚ÜíI")
372        AOT_show ‚ÄπPropositional([F])‚Ä∫ if ‚Äπx[F]‚Ä∫ for F
373          using 1[THEN "‚â°E"(1), OF that]
374          by (metis "‚â°‚á©d‚á©fI" "prop-prop1")
375      qed
376      AOT_show ‚ÄπSituation(x) & ‚àÄp (x ‚ä® p)‚Ä∫
377      proof (safe intro!: "&I" 2 0[THEN "&E"(1)] GEN "‚ÜíI")
378        AOT_have ‚Äπx[Œªy p] ‚â° ‚àÉq [Œªy p] = [Œªy q]‚Ä∫ for p
379          by (rule 1[unvarify F, where œÑ="¬´[Œªy p]¬ª"]) "cqt:2[lambda]"
380        moreover AOT_have ‚Äπ‚àÉq [Œªy p] = [Œªy q]‚Ä∫ for p
381          by (rule "‚àÉI"(2)[where Œ≤=p])
382             (simp add: "rule=I:1" "prop-prop2:2")
383        ultimately AOT_have ‚Äπx[Œªy p]‚Ä∫ for p by (metis "‚â°E"(2))
384        AOT_thus ‚Äπx ‚ä® p‚Ä∫ for p
385          by (metis "2" "‚â°E"(2) lem1 "‚ÜíE")
386      qed
387    qed
388  }
389next
390  AOT_show ‚Äπ‚àÉ!x ([A!]x & ‚àÄF (x[F] ‚â° ‚àÉp F = [Œªy p]))‚Ä∫
391    by (simp add: "A-objects!")
392qed

406AOT_theorem "null-triv-sc:1": ‚ÄπNullSituation(x) ‚Üí ‚ñ°NullSituation(x)‚Ä∫
407proof(safe intro!: "‚ÜíI" dest!: "df-null-trivial:1"[THEN "‚â°‚á©d‚á©fE"]; frule "&E"(1); drule "&E"(2))
408  AOT_assume 1: ‚Äπ¬¨‚àÉp (x ‚ä® p)‚Ä∫
409  AOT_assume 0: ‚ÄπSituation(x)‚Ä∫
410  AOT_hence ‚Äπ‚ñ°Situation(x)‚Ä∫ by (metis "‚â°E"(1) "possit-sit:1")
411  moreover AOT_have ‚Äπ‚ñ°¬¨‚àÉp (x ‚ä® p)‚Ä∫
412  proof(rule "raa-cor:1")
413    AOT_assume ‚Äπ¬¨‚ñ°¬¨‚àÉp (x ‚ä® p)‚Ä∫
414    AOT_hence ‚Äπ‚óá‚àÉp (x ‚ä® p)‚Ä∫
415      by (metis "‚â°‚á©d‚á©fI" "conventions:5")
416    AOT_hence ‚Äπ‚àÉp ‚óá(x ‚ä® p)‚Ä∫ by (metis "BF‚óá" "‚ÜíE")
417    then AOT_obtain p where ‚Äπ‚óá(x ‚ä® p)‚Ä∫ using "‚àÉE"[rotated] by blast
418    AOT_hence ‚Äπx ‚ä® p‚Ä∫
419      by (metis "‚â°E"(1) "lem2:2"[unconstrain s, THEN "‚ÜíE", OF 0])
420    AOT_hence ‚Äπ‚àÉp x ‚ä® p‚Ä∫ using "‚àÉI" by fast
421    AOT_thus ‚Äπ‚àÉp x ‚ä® p & ¬¨‚àÉp x ‚ä® p‚Ä∫ using 1 "&I" by blast
422  qed
423  ultimately AOT_have 2: ‚Äπ‚ñ°(Situation(x) & ¬¨‚àÉp x ‚ä® p)‚Ä∫
424    by (metis "KBasic:3" "&I" "‚â°E"(2))
425  AOT_show ‚Äπ‚ñ°NullSituation(x)‚Ä∫
426    by (AOT_subst ‚Äπ¬´NullSituation(x)¬ª‚Ä∫ ‚Äπ¬´Situation(x) & ¬¨‚àÉp x ‚ä® p¬ª‚Ä∫)
427       (auto simp: "df-null-trivial:1" "‚â°Df" 2)
428qed

431AOT_theorem "null-triv-sc:2": ‚ÄπTrivialSituation(x) ‚Üí ‚ñ°TrivialSituation(x)‚Ä∫

459AOT_theorem "null-triv-facts:1": ‚ÄπNullSituation(x) ‚â° Null(x)‚Ä∫
460proof (safe intro!: "‚â°I" "‚ÜíI" "df-null-uni:1"[THEN "‚â°‚á©d‚á©fI"] "df-null-trivial:1"[THEN "‚â°‚á©d‚á©fI"]
461            dest!: "df-null-uni:1"[THEN "‚â°‚á©d‚á©fE"] "df-null-trivial:1"[THEN "‚â°‚á©d‚á©fE"])
462  AOT_assume 0: ‚ÄπSituation(x) & ¬¨‚àÉp x ‚ä® p‚Ä∫
463  AOT_have 1: ‚Äπx[F] ‚Üí ‚àÉp F = [Œªy p]‚Ä∫ for F
464    using 0[THEN "&E"(1), THEN situations[THEN "‚â°‚á©d‚á©fE"], THEN "&E"(2), THEN "‚àÄE"(2)]
465    by (metis "‚â°‚á©d‚á©fE" "deduction-theorem" "prop-prop1" "‚ÜíE")
466  AOT_show ‚ÄπA!x & ¬¨‚àÉF x[F]‚Ä∫
467  proof (safe intro!: "&I" 0[THEN "&E"(1), THEN situations[THEN "‚â°‚á©d‚á©fE"], THEN "&E"(1)]; rule "raa-cor:2")
468    AOT_assume ‚Äπ‚àÉF x[F]‚Ä∫
469    then AOT_obtain F where F_prop: ‚Äπx[F]‚Ä∫ using "‚àÉE"[rotated] by blast
470    AOT_hence ‚Äπ‚àÉp F = [Œªy p]‚Ä∫ using 1[THEN "‚ÜíE"] by blast
471    then AOT_obtain p where ‚ÄπF = [Œªy p]‚Ä∫ using "‚àÉE"[rotated] by blast
472    AOT_hence ‚Äπx[Œªy p]‚Ä∫ by (metis "rule=E" F_prop)
473    AOT_hence ‚Äπx ‚ä® p‚Ä∫ using lem1[THEN "‚ÜíE", OF 0[THEN "&E"(1)], THEN "‚â°E"(2)] by blast
474    AOT_hence ‚Äπ‚àÉp x ‚ä® p‚Ä∫ by (rule "‚àÉI")
475    AOT_thus ‚Äπ‚àÉp x ‚ä® p & ¬¨‚àÉp x ‚ä® p‚Ä∫ using 0[THEN "&E"(2)] "&I" by blast
476  qed
477next
478  AOT_assume 0: ‚ÄπA!x & ¬¨‚àÉF x[F]‚Ä∫
479  AOT_have ‚ÄπSituation(x)‚Ä∫
480    apply (rule situations[THEN "‚â°‚á©d‚á©fI", OF "&I", OF 0[THEN "&E"(1)]]; rule GEN)
481    using 0[THEN "&E"(2)] by (metis "deduction-theorem" "existential:2[const_var]" "raa-cor:3") 
482  moreover AOT_have ‚Äπ¬¨‚àÉp x ‚ä® p‚Ä∫
483  proof (rule "raa-cor:2")
484    AOT_assume ‚Äπ‚àÉp x ‚ä® p‚Ä∫
485    then AOT_obtain p where ‚Äπx ‚ä® p‚Ä∫ by (metis "instantiation")
486    AOT_hence ‚Äπx[Œªy p]‚Ä∫ by (metis "‚â°‚á©d‚á©fE" "&E"(2) "prop-enc" "true-in-s")
487    AOT_hence ‚Äπ‚àÉF x[F]‚Ä∫ by (rule "‚àÉI") "cqt:2[lambda]"
488    AOT_thus ‚Äπ‚àÉF x[F] & ¬¨‚àÉF x[F]‚Ä∫ using 0[THEN "&E"(2)] "&I" by blast
489  qed
490  ultimately AOT_show ‚ÄπSituation(x) & ¬¨‚àÉp x ‚ä® p‚Ä∫ using "&I" by blast
491qed

493AOT_theorem "null-triv-facts:2": ‚Äπ‚ùôs‚á©‚àÖ = a‚á©‚àÖ‚Ä∫
494  apply (rule "=‚á©d‚á©fI"(2)[OF "df-the-null-sit:1"])
495   apply (fact "thm-null-trivial:3")
496  apply (rule "=‚á©d‚á©fI"(2)[OF "df-null-uni-terms:1"])

503AOT_theorem "null-triv-facts:3": ‚Äπ‚ùôs‚á©V ‚â† a‚á©V‚Ä∫
504proof(rule "=-infix"[THEN "‚â°‚á©d‚á©fI"])
505  AOT_have ‚ÄπUniversal(a‚á©V)‚Ä∫
506    by (simp add: "null-uni-facts:4")
507  AOT_hence 0: ‚Äπa‚á©V[A!]‚Ä∫
508    using "df-null-uni:2"[THEN "‚â°‚á©d‚á©fE"] "&E" "‚àÄE"(1)
509    by (metis "cqt:5:a" "vdash-properties:10" "vdash-properties:1[2]")
510  moreover AOT_have 1: ‚Äπ¬¨‚ùôs‚á©V[A!]‚Ä∫
511  proof(rule "raa-cor:2")
512    AOT_have ‚ÄπSituation(‚ùôs‚á©V)‚Ä∫
513      using "‚â°‚á©d‚á©fE" "&E"(1) "df-null-trivial:2" "null-triv-sc:4" by blast
514    AOT_hence ‚Äπ‚àÄF (‚ùôs‚á©V[F] ‚Üí Propositional([F]))‚Ä∫
515      by (metis "‚â°‚á©d‚á©fE" "&E"(2) situations)
516    moreover AOT_assume ‚Äπ‚ùôs‚á©V[A!]‚Ä∫
517    ultimately AOT_have ‚ÄπPropositional(A!)‚Ä∫ using "‚àÄE"(1)[rotated, OF "oa-exist:2"] "‚ÜíE" by blast
518    AOT_thus ‚ÄπPropositional(A!) & ¬¨Propositional(A!)‚Ä∫ using "prop-in-f:4:d" "&I" by blast
519  qed
520  AOT_show ‚Äπ¬¨(‚ùôs‚á©V = a‚á©V)‚Ä∫
521  proof (rule "raa-cor:2")
522    AOT_assume ‚Äπ‚ùôs‚á©V = a‚á©V‚Ä∫
523    AOT_hence ‚Äπ‚ùôs‚á©V[A!]‚Ä∫ using 0 "rule=E" id_sym by fast
524    AOT_thus ‚Äπ‚ùôs‚á©V[A!] & ¬¨‚ùôs‚á©V[A!]‚Ä∫ using 1 "&I" by blast
525  qed
526qed

528definition ConditionOnPropositionalProperties :: ‚Äπ(<Œ∫> ‚áí ùóà) ‚áí bool‚Ä∫ where
529  "cond-prop": ‚ÄπConditionOnPropositionalProperties ‚â° Œª œÜ . ‚àÄ v . [v ‚ä® ‚àÄF (œÜ{F} ‚Üí Propositional([F]))]‚Ä∫
530
531syntax ConditionOnPropositionalProperties :: ‚Äπid_position ‚áí AOT_prop‚Ä∫ ("CONDITION'_ON'_PROPOSITIONAL'_PROPERTIES'(_')")
532
533AOT_theorem "cond-prop[E]":
534  assumes ‚ÄπCONDITION_ON_PROPOSITIONAL_PROPERTIES(œÜ)‚Ä∫
535  shows ‚Äπ‚àÄF (œÜ{F} ‚Üí Propositional([F]))‚Ä∫
536  using assms[unfolded "cond-prop"] by auto

538AOT_theorem "cond-prop[I]":
539  assumes ‚Äπ‚ùô‚ä¢‚á©‚ñ° ‚àÄF (œÜ{F} ‚Üí Propositional([F]))‚Ä∫
540  shows ‚ÄπCONDITION_ON_PROPOSITIONAL_PROPERTIES(œÜ)‚Ä∫
541  using assms "cond-prop" by metis

543AOT_theorem "pre-comp-sit":
544  assumes ‚ÄπCONDITION_ON_PROPOSITIONAL_PROPERTIES(œÜ)‚Ä∫
545  shows ‚Äπ(Situation(x) & ‚àÄF (x[F] ‚â° œÜ{F})) ‚â° (A!x & ‚àÄF (x[F] ‚â° œÜ{F}))‚Ä∫
546proof(rule "‚â°I"; rule "‚ÜíI")
547  AOT_assume ‚ÄπSituation(x) & ‚àÄF (x[F] ‚â° œÜ{F})‚Ä∫
548  AOT_thus ‚ÄπA!x & ‚àÄF (x[F] ‚â° œÜ{F})‚Ä∫
549    using "&E" situations[THEN "‚â°‚á©d‚á©fE"] "&I" by blast
550next
551  AOT_assume 0: ‚ÄπA!x & ‚àÄF (x[F] ‚â° œÜ{F})‚Ä∫
552  AOT_show ‚ÄπSituation(x) & ‚àÄF (x[F] ‚â° œÜ{F})‚Ä∫
553  proof (safe intro!: situations[THEN "‚â°‚á©d‚á©fI"] "&I")
554    AOT_show ‚ÄπA!x‚Ä∫ using 0[THEN "&E"(1)].
555  next
556    AOT_show ‚Äπ‚àÄF (x[F] ‚Üí Propositional([F]))‚Ä∫
557    proof(rule GEN; rule "‚ÜíI")
558      fix F
559      AOT_assume ‚Äπx[F]‚Ä∫
560      AOT_hence ‚ÄπœÜ{F}‚Ä∫ using 0[THEN "&E"(2)] "‚àÄE" "‚â°E" by blast
561      AOT_thus ‚ÄπPropositional([F])‚Ä∫ using "cond-prop[E]"[OF assms] "‚àÄE" "‚ÜíE" by blast
562    qed
563  next
564    AOT_show ‚Äπ‚àÄF (x[F] ‚â° œÜ{F})‚Ä∫ using 0 "&E" by blast
565  qed
566qed

600AOT_define actual :: ‚ÄπœÑ ‚áí œÜ‚Ä∫ (‚ÄπActual'(_')‚Ä∫)
601  ‚ÄπActual(s) ‚â°‚á©d‚á©f ‚àÄp (s ‚ä® p ‚Üí p)‚Ä∫
602
603AOT_theorem "act-and-not-pos": ‚Äπ‚àÉs (Actual(s) & ‚óá¬¨Actual(s))‚Ä∫
604proof -
605  AOT_obtain q‚á©1 where q‚á©1_prop: ‚Äπq‚á©1 & ‚óá¬¨q‚á©1‚Ä∫
606    by (metis "‚â°‚á©d‚á©fE" "instantiation" "cont-tf:1" "cont-tf-thm:1")
607  AOT_have ‚Äπ‚àÉs (‚àÄF (s[F] ‚â° F = [Œªy q‚á©1]))‚Ä∫
608  proof (safe intro!: "comp-sit:1" "cond-prop[I]" GEN "‚ÜíI")
609    AOT_modally_strict {
610      AOT_show ‚ÄπPropositional([F])‚Ä∫ if ‚ÄπF = [Œªy q‚á©1]‚Ä∫ for F
611        using "‚â°‚á©d‚á©fI" "existential:2[const_var]" "prop-prop1" that by fastforce
612    }
613  qed
614  then AOT_obtain s‚á©1 where s_prop: ‚Äπ‚àÄF (s‚á©1[F] ‚â° F = [Œªy q‚á©1])‚Ä∫
615    using "Situation.‚àÉE"[rotated] by meson
616  AOT_have ‚ÄπActual(s‚á©1)‚Ä∫
617  proof(safe intro!: actual[THEN "‚â°‚á©d‚á©fI"] "&I" GEN "‚ÜíI" s_prop Situation.œà)
618    fix p
619    AOT_assume ‚Äπs‚á©1 ‚ä® p‚Ä∫
620    AOT_hence ‚Äπs‚á©1[Œªy p]‚Ä∫
621      by (metis "‚â°‚á©d‚á©fE" "&E"(2) "prop-enc" "true-in-s")
622    AOT_hence ‚Äπ[Œªy p] = [Œªy q‚á©1]‚Ä∫
623      by (rule s_prop[THEN "‚àÄE"(1), THEN "‚â°E"(1), rotated]) "cqt:2[lambda]"
624    AOT_hence ‚Äπp = q‚á©1‚Ä∫ by (metis "‚â°E"(2) "p-identity-thm2:3")
625    AOT_thus ‚Äπp‚Ä∫ using q‚á©1_prop[THEN "&E"(1)] "rule=E" id_sym by fast
626  qed
627  moreover AOT_have ‚Äπ‚óá¬¨Actual(s‚á©1)‚Ä∫
628  proof(rule "raa-cor:1"; drule "KBasic:12"[THEN "‚â°E"(2)])
629    AOT_assume ‚Äπ‚ñ°Actual(s‚á©1)‚Ä∫
630    AOT_hence ‚Äπ‚ñ°(Situation(s‚á©1) & ‚àÄp (s‚á©1 ‚ä® p ‚Üí p))‚Ä∫
631      using actual[THEN "‚â°Df", THEN "conventions:3"[THEN "‚â°‚á©d‚á©fE"], THEN "&E"(1), THEN RM, THEN "‚ÜíE"] by blast
632    AOT_hence ‚Äπ‚ñ°‚àÄp (s‚á©1 ‚ä® p ‚Üí p)‚Ä∫ by (metis "RM:1" "Conjunction Simplification"(2) "vdash-properties:10")
633    AOT_hence ‚Äπ‚àÄp ‚ñ°(s‚á©1 ‚ä® p ‚Üí p)‚Ä∫ by (metis "CBF" "vdash-properties:10")
634    AOT_hence ‚Äπ‚ñ°(s‚á©1 ‚ä® q‚á©1 ‚Üí q‚á©1)‚Ä∫ using "‚àÄE" by blast
635    AOT_hence ‚Äπ‚ñ°s‚á©1 ‚ä® q‚á©1 ‚Üí ‚ñ°q‚á©1‚Ä∫ by (metis "‚ÜíE" "qml:1" "vdash-properties:1[2]")
636    moreover AOT_have ‚Äπs‚á©1 ‚ä® q‚á©1‚Ä∫
637      using s_prop[THEN "‚àÄE"(1), THEN "‚â°E"(2), THEN lem1[THEN "‚ÜíE", OF Situation.œà, THEN "‚â°E"(2)]]
638            "rule=I:1" "prop-prop2:2" by blast
639    ultimately AOT_have ‚Äπ‚ñ°q‚á©1‚Ä∫
640      using "‚â°‚á©d‚á©fE" "&E"(1) "‚â°E"(1) "lem2:1" "true-in-s" "vdash-properties:10" by fast
641    AOT_thus ‚Äπ‚óá¬¨q‚á©1 & ¬¨‚óá¬¨q‚á©1‚Ä∫ using "KBasic:12"[THEN "‚â°E"(1)] q‚á©1_prop[THEN "&E"(2)] "&I" by blast
642  qed
643  ultimately AOT_have ‚Äπ(Actual(s‚á©1) & ‚óá¬¨Actual(s‚á©1))‚Ä∫ using s_prop "&I" by blast
644  thus ?thesis by (rule "Situation.‚àÉI")
645qed

647AOT_theorem "actual-s:1": ‚Äπ‚àÉs Actual(s)‚Ä∫

655AOT_theorem "actual-s:2": ‚Äπ‚àÉs ¬¨Actual(s)‚Ä∫

658    using "‚â°‚á©d‚á©fE" "&E"(1) "df-null-trivial:2" "null-triv-sc:4" by blast

664      by (metis "instantiation" "existential:1" "log-prop-prop:2" "non-contradiction")
665    AOT_have ‚Äπ‚ùôs‚á©V ‚ä® p‚á©1‚Ä∫
666      using "null-triv-sc:4"[THEN "‚â°‚á©d‚á©fE"[OF "df-null-trivial:2"], THEN "&E"(2)] "‚àÄE" by blast
667    AOT_hence ‚Äπp‚á©1‚Ä∫ using 0[THEN actual[THEN "‚â°‚á©d‚á©fE"], THEN "&E"(2), THEN "‚àÄE"(2), THEN "‚ÜíE"]
668      by blast
669    AOT_thus ‚Äπp & ¬¨p‚Ä∫ for p using notp‚á©1 by (metis "raa-cor:3")
670  qed
671next
672  AOT_show ‚Äπ‚ùôs‚á©V‚Üì‚Ä∫

676AOT_theorem "actual-s:3": ‚Äπ‚àÉp‚àÄs(Actual(s) ‚Üí ¬¨s ‚ä® p)‚Ä∫
677proof -

679    by (metis "instantiation" "existential:1" "log-prop-prop:2" "non-contradiction")

686    AOT_thus ‚Äπp‚á©1 & ¬¨p‚á©1‚Ä∫ using notp‚á©1 "&I" by simp
687  qed
688  thus ?thesis by (rule "‚àÉI")
689qed

691AOT_theorem comp: ‚Äπ‚àÉs (s' ‚ä¥ s & s'' ‚ä¥ s & ‚àÄs''' (s' ‚ä¥ s''' & s'' ‚ä¥ s''' ‚Üí s ‚ä¥ s'''))‚Ä∫
692proof -
693  have cond_prop: ‚ÄπConditionOnPropositionalProperties (Œª Œ† . ¬´s'[Œ†] ‚à® s''[Œ†]¬ª)‚Ä∫
694  proof(safe intro!: "cond-prop[I]" GEN "oth-class-taut:8:c"[THEN "‚ÜíE", THEN "‚ÜíE"]; rule "‚ÜíI")
695    AOT_modally_strict {
696      fix F
697      AOT_have ‚ÄπSituation(s')‚Ä∫
698        by (simp add: Situation.restricted_var_condition)
699      AOT_hence ‚Äπs'[F] ‚Üí Propositional([F])‚Ä∫
700        using "situations"[THEN "‚â°‚á©d‚á©fE", THEN "&E"(2), THEN "‚àÄE"(2)] by blast
701      moreover AOT_assume ‚Äπs'[F]‚Ä∫
702      ultimately AOT_show ‚ÄπPropositional([F])‚Ä∫
703        using "‚ÜíE" by blast
704    }
705  next
706    AOT_modally_strict {
707      fix F
708      AOT_have ‚ÄπSituation(s'')‚Ä∫
709        by (simp add: Situation.restricted_var_condition)
710      AOT_hence ‚Äπs''[F] ‚Üí Propositional([F])‚Ä∫
711        using "situations"[THEN "‚â°‚á©d‚á©fE", THEN "&E"(2), THEN "‚àÄE"(2)] by blast
712      moreover AOT_assume ‚Äπs''[F]‚Ä∫
713      ultimately AOT_show ‚ÄπPropositional([F])‚Ä∫
714        using "‚ÜíE" by blast
715    }
716  qed
717  AOT_obtain s‚á©3 where Œ∏: ‚Äπ‚àÄF (s‚á©3[F] ‚â° s'[F] ‚à® s''[F])‚Ä∫
718    using "comp-sit:1"[OF cond_prop] "Situation.‚àÉE"[rotated] by meson
719  AOT_have ‚Äπs' ‚ä¥ s‚á©3 & s'' ‚ä¥ s‚á©3 & ‚àÄs''' (s' ‚ä¥ s''' & s'' ‚ä¥ s''' ‚Üí s‚á©3 ‚ä¥ s''')‚Ä∫
720  proof(safe intro!: "&I" "‚â°‚á©d‚á©fI"[OF "true-in-s"] "‚â°‚á©d‚á©fI"[OF "prop-enc"]
721                     "Situation.GEN" "GEN"[where 'a=ùóà] "‚ÜíI" "sit-part-whole"[THEN "‚â°‚á©d‚á©fI"]
722                     Situation.restricted_var_condition "cqt:2[const_var]"[axiom_inst])
723    fix p
724    AOT_assume ‚Äπs' ‚ä® p‚Ä∫
725    AOT_hence ‚Äπs'[Œªx p]‚Ä∫
726      by (metis "&E"(2) "prop-enc" "‚â°‚á©d‚á©fE" "true-in-s")
727    AOT_thus ‚Äπs‚á©3[Œªx p]‚Ä∫
728      using Œ∏[THEN "‚àÄE"(1),OF "prop-prop2:2", THEN "‚â°E"(2), OF "‚à®I"(1)] by blast
729  next
730    fix p
731    AOT_assume ‚Äπs'' ‚ä® p‚Ä∫
732    AOT_hence ‚Äπs''[Œªx p]‚Ä∫
733      by (metis "&E"(2) "prop-enc" "‚â°‚á©d‚á©fE" "true-in-s")
734    AOT_thus ‚Äπs‚á©3[Œªx p]‚Ä∫
735      using Œ∏[THEN "‚àÄE"(1),OF "prop-prop2:2", THEN "‚â°E"(2), OF "‚à®I"(2)] by blast
736  next
737    fix s p
738    AOT_assume 0: ‚Äπs' ‚ä¥ s & s'' ‚ä¥ s‚Ä∫
739    AOT_assume ‚Äπs‚á©3 ‚ä® p‚Ä∫
740    AOT_hence ‚Äπs‚á©3[Œªx p]‚Ä∫
741      by (metis "&E"(2) "prop-enc" "‚â°‚á©d‚á©fE" "true-in-s")
742    AOT_hence ‚Äπs'[Œªx p] ‚à® s''[Œªx p]‚Ä∫
743      using Œ∏[THEN "‚àÄE"(1),OF "prop-prop2:2", THEN "‚â°E"(1)] by blast
744    moreover {
745      AOT_assume ‚Äπs'[Œªx p]‚Ä∫
746      AOT_hence ‚Äπs' ‚ä® p‚Ä∫
747        by (safe intro!: "prop-enc"[THEN "‚â°‚á©d‚á©fI"] "true-in-s"[THEN "‚â°‚á©d‚á©fI"] "&I"
748                         Situation.œà "cqt:2[const_var]"[axiom_inst])
749      moreover AOT_have ‚Äπs' ‚ä® p ‚Üí s ‚ä® p‚Ä∫
750        using "sit-part-whole"[THEN "‚â°‚á©d‚á©fE", THEN "&E"(2)] 0[THEN "&E"(1)] "‚àÄE"(2) by blast
751      ultimately AOT_have ‚Äπs ‚ä® p‚Ä∫
752        using "‚ÜíE" by blast
753      AOT_hence ‚Äπs[Œªx p]‚Ä∫
754        using "true-in-s"[THEN "‚â°‚á©d‚á©fE"] "prop-enc"[THEN "‚â°‚á©d‚á©fE"] "&E" by blast
755    }
756    moreover {
757      AOT_assume ‚Äπs''[Œªx p]‚Ä∫
758      AOT_hence ‚Äπs'' ‚ä® p‚Ä∫
759        by (safe intro!: "prop-enc"[THEN "‚â°‚á©d‚á©fI"] "true-in-s"[THEN "‚â°‚á©d‚á©fI"] "&I"
760                         Situation.œà "cqt:2[const_var]"[axiom_inst])
761      moreover AOT_have ‚Äπs'' ‚ä® p ‚Üí s ‚ä® p‚Ä∫
762        using "sit-part-whole"[THEN "‚â°‚á©d‚á©fE", THEN "&E"(2)] 0[THEN "&E"(2)] "‚àÄE"(2) by blast
763      ultimately AOT_have ‚Äπs ‚ä® p‚Ä∫
764        using "‚ÜíE" by blast
765      AOT_hence ‚Äπs[Œªx p]‚Ä∫
766        using "true-in-s"[THEN "‚â°‚á©d‚á©fE"] "prop-enc"[THEN "‚â°‚á©d‚á©fE"] "&E" by blast
767    }
768    ultimately AOT_show ‚Äπs[Œªx p]‚Ä∫
769      by (metis "‚à®E"(1) "‚ÜíI")
770  qed
771  thus ?thesis
772    using "Situation.‚àÉI" by fast
773qed

775AOT_theorem "act-sit:1": ‚ÄπActual(s) ‚Üí (s ‚ä® p ‚Üí [Œªy p]s)‚Ä∫
776proof (safe intro!: "‚ÜíI")
777  AOT_assume ‚ÄπActual(s)‚Ä∫
778  AOT_hence p if ‚Äπs ‚ä® p‚Ä∫ using actual[THEN "‚â°‚á©d‚á©fE", THEN "&E"(2), THEN "‚àÄE"(2), THEN "‚ÜíE"] that by blast
779  moreover AOT_assume ‚Äπs ‚ä® p‚Ä∫
780  ultimately AOT_have p by blast
781  AOT_thus ‚Äπ[Œªy p]s‚Ä∫
782    by (safe intro!: "Œ≤‚ÜêC"(1) "cqt:2")
783qed

785AOT_theorem "act-sit:2": ‚Äπ(Actual(s') & Actual(s'')) ‚Üí ‚àÉx (Actual(x) & s' ‚ä¥ x & s'' ‚ä¥ x)‚Ä∫
786proof(rule "‚ÜíI"; frule "&E"(1); drule "&E"(2))
787  AOT_assume act_s': ‚ÄπActual(s')‚Ä∫

1148AOT_theorem "sit-classical:6":

1373AOT_theorem "world=maxpos:2": ‚ÄπPossibleWorld(x) ‚â° Maximal(x) & Possible(x)‚Ä∫
1374proof(safe intro!: "‚â°I" "‚ÜíI" "&I" "world-pos"[unconstrain w, THEN "‚ÜíE"] "world-max"[unconstrain w, THEN "‚ÜíE"]; frule "&E"(2); drule "&E"(1))
1375  AOT_assume pos_x: ‚ÄπPossible(x)‚Ä∫
1376  AOT_have ‚Äπ‚óá(Situation(x) & ‚àÄp(x ‚ä® p ‚Üí p))‚Ä∫
1377    apply (AOT_subst_rev ‚Äπ¬´Actual(x)¬ª‚Ä∫ ‚Äπ¬´Situation(x) & ‚àÄp(x ‚ä® p ‚Üí p)¬ª‚Ä∫)

1379    using "‚â°‚á©d‚á©fE" "&E"(2) pos pos_x by blast
1380  AOT_hence 0: ‚Äπ‚óá‚àÄp(x ‚ä® p ‚Üí p)‚Ä∫
1381    by (metis "KBasic2:3" "&E"(2) "vdash-properties:6")
1382  AOT_assume max_x: ‚ÄπMaximal(x)‚Ä∫
1383  AOT_hence sit_x: ‚ÄπSituation(x)‚Ä∫ by (metis "‚â°‚á©d‚á©fE" max_x "&E"(1) max)
1384  AOT_have ‚Äπ‚ñ°Maximal(x)‚Ä∫ using "world=maxpos:1"[THEN "‚ÜíE", OF max_x] by simp
1385  moreover AOT_have ‚Äπ‚ñ°Maximal(x) ‚Üí ‚ñ°(‚àÄp(x ‚ä® p ‚Üí p) ‚Üí ‚àÄp (x ‚ä® p ‚â° p))‚Ä∫

1388      fix p
1389      AOT_assume 0: ‚ÄπMaximal(x)‚Ä∫
1390      AOT_assume 1: ‚Äπ‚àÄp (x ‚ä® p ‚Üí p)‚Ä∫
1391      AOT_show ‚Äπx ‚ä® p ‚â° p‚Ä∫
1392      proof(safe intro!: "‚â°I" "‚ÜíI" 1[THEN "‚àÄE"(2), THEN "‚ÜíE"]; rule "raa-cor:1")
1393        AOT_assume ‚Äπ¬¨x ‚ä® p‚Ä∫
1394        AOT_hence ‚Äπx ‚ä® ¬¨p‚Ä∫
1395          using 0[THEN "‚â°‚á©d‚á©fE"[OF max], THEN "&E"(2), THEN "‚àÄE"(2)]
1396                1 by (metis "‚à®E"(2))
1397        AOT_hence ‚Äπ¬¨p‚Ä∫ using 1[THEN "‚àÄE"(1), OF "log-prop-prop:2", THEN "‚ÜíE"] by blast
1398        moreover AOT_assume p
1399        ultimately AOT_show ‚Äπp & ¬¨p‚Ä∫ using "&I" by blast
1400      qed
1401    }
1402  qed
1403  ultimately AOT_have ‚Äπ‚ñ°(‚àÄp(x ‚ä® p ‚Üí p) ‚Üí ‚àÄp (x ‚ä® p ‚â° p))‚Ä∫ using "‚ÜíE" by blast
1404  AOT_hence ‚Äπ‚óá‚àÄp(x ‚ä® p ‚Üí p) ‚Üí ‚óá‚àÄp(x ‚ä® p ‚â° p)‚Ä∫ by (metis "KBasic:13"[THEN "‚ÜíE"])
1405  AOT_hence ‚Äπ‚óá‚àÄp(x ‚ä® p ‚â° p)‚Ä∫ using 0 "‚ÜíE" by blast
1406  AOT_thus ‚ÄπPossibleWorld(x)‚Ä∫ using "‚â°‚á©d‚á©fI"[OF "world:1", OF "&I", OF sit_x] by blast

1479AOT_theorem "coherent:1": ‚Äπw ‚ä® ¬¨p ‚â° ¬¨w ‚ä® p‚Ä∫
1480proof(safe intro!: "‚â°I" "‚ÜíI")
1481  AOT_assume 1: ‚Äπw ‚ä® ¬¨p‚Ä∫
1482  AOT_show ‚Äπ¬¨w ‚ä® p‚Ä∫
1483  proof(rule "raa-cor:2")
1484    AOT_assume ‚Äπw ‚ä® p‚Ä∫
1485    AOT_hence ‚Äπw ‚ä® p & w ‚ä® ¬¨p‚Ä∫ using 1 "&I" by blast
1486    AOT_hence ‚Äπ‚àÉq (w ‚ä® q & w ‚ä® ¬¨q)‚Ä∫ by (rule "‚àÉI")
1487    moreover AOT_have ‚Äπ¬¨‚àÉq (w ‚ä® q & w ‚ä® ¬¨q)‚Ä∫
1488      using "world-cons:1"[THEN "‚â°‚á©d‚á©fE"[OF cons], THEN "&E"(2)].
1489    ultimately AOT_show ‚Äπ‚àÉq (w ‚ä® q & w ‚ä® ¬¨q) & ¬¨‚àÉq (w ‚ä® q & w ‚ä® ¬¨q)‚Ä∫ using "&I" by blast
1490  qed
1491next
1492  AOT_assume ‚Äπ¬¨w ‚ä® p‚Ä∫
1493  AOT_thus ‚Äπw ‚ä® ¬¨p‚Ä∫
1494    using "world-max"[THEN "‚â°‚á©d‚á©fE"[OF max], THEN "&E"(2)]
1495    by (metis "‚à®E"(2) "log-prop-prop:2" "rule-ui:1")
1496qed

1501AOT_theorem "act-world:1": ‚Äπ‚àÉw ‚àÄp (w ‚ä® p ‚â° p)‚Ä∫
1502proof -
1503  AOT_obtain s where s_prop: ‚Äπ‚àÄp (s ‚ä® p ‚â° p)‚Ä∫ using "sit-classical:6" "Situation.‚àÉE"[rotated] by meson
1504  AOT_hence ‚Äπ‚óá‚àÄp (s ‚ä® p ‚â° p)‚Ä∫
1505    by (metis "T‚óá" "vdash-properties:10")
1506  AOT_hence ‚ÄπPossibleWorld(s)‚Ä∫
1507    using "world:1"[THEN "‚â°‚á©d‚á©fI"] Situation.œà "&I" by blast
1508  AOT_hence ‚ÄπPossibleWorld(s) & ‚àÄp (s ‚ä® p ‚â° p)‚Ä∫ using "&I" s_prop by blast
1509  thus ?thesis by (rule "‚àÉI")
1510qed

1512AOT_theorem "act-world:2": ‚Äπ‚àÉ!w Actual(w)‚Ä∫
1513proof -
1514  AOT_obtain w where w_prop: ‚Äπ‚àÄp (w ‚ä® p ‚â° p)‚Ä∫ using "act-world:1" "PossibleWorld.‚àÉE"[rotated] by meson
1515  AOT_have sit_s: ‚ÄπSituation(w)‚Ä∫ using PossibleWorld.œà "world:1"[THEN "‚â°‚á©d‚á©fE", THEN "&E"(1)] by blast
1516  show ?thesis
1517  proof (safe intro!: "uniqueness:1"[THEN "‚â°‚á©d‚á©fI"] "‚àÉI"(2) "&I" GEN "‚ÜíI"
1518                      PossibleWorld.œà actual[THEN "‚â°‚á©d‚á©fI"] sit_s "sit-identity"[unconstrain s, unconstrain s', THEN "‚ÜíE", THEN "‚ÜíE", THEN "‚â°E"(2)] "‚â°I"
1519                      w_prop[THEN "‚àÄE"(2), THEN "‚â°E"(1)])
1520    AOT_show ‚ÄπPossibleWorld(w)‚Ä∫ using PossibleWorld.œà.
1521  next
1522    AOT_show ‚ÄπSituation(w)‚Ä∫
1523      by (simp add: sit_s)
1524  next
1525    fix y p
1526    AOT_assume w_asm: ‚ÄπPossibleWorld(y) & Actual(y)‚Ä∫
1527    AOT_assume ‚Äπw ‚ä® p‚Ä∫
1528    AOT_hence p: ‚Äπp‚Ä∫ using w_prop[THEN "‚àÄE"(2), THEN "‚â°E"(1)] by blast
1529    AOT_show ‚Äπy ‚ä® p‚Ä∫
1530    proof(rule "raa-cor:1")
1531      AOT_assume ‚Äπ¬¨y ‚ä® p‚Ä∫
1532      AOT_hence ‚Äπy ‚ä® ¬¨p‚Ä∫ by (metis "coherent:1"[unconstrain w, THEN "‚ÜíE"] "&E"(1) "‚â°E"(2) w_asm)
1533      AOT_hence ‚Äπ¬¨p‚Ä∫
1534        using w_asm[THEN "&E"(2), THEN actual[THEN "‚â°‚á©d‚á©fE"], THEN "&E"(2), THEN "‚àÄE"(1), rotated, OF "log-prop-prop:2"]
1535              "‚ÜíE" by blast
1536      AOT_thus ‚Äπp & ¬¨p‚Ä∫ using p "&I" by blast
1537    qed
1538  next
1539    AOT_show ‚Äπw ‚ä® p‚Ä∫ if ‚Äπy ‚ä® p‚Ä∫ and ‚ÄπPossibleWorld(y) & Actual(y)‚Ä∫ for p y
1540      using that(2)[THEN "&E"(2), THEN actual[THEN "‚â°‚á©d‚á©fE"], THEN "&E"(2), THEN "‚àÄE"(2),
1541                  THEN "‚ÜíE", OF that(1)]
1542            w_prop[THEN "‚àÄE"(2), THEN "‚â°E"(2)] by blast
1543  next
1544    AOT_show ‚ÄπSituation(y)‚Ä∫ if ‚ÄπPossibleWorld(y) & Actual(y)‚Ä∫ for y
1545      using that[THEN "&E"(1)] "world:1"[THEN "‚â°‚á©d‚á©fE", THEN "&E"(1)] by blast
1546  next
1547    AOT_show ‚ÄπSituation(w)‚Ä∫
1548      using sit_s by blast
1549  qed(simp)
1550qed

1558AOT_act_theorem "T-world:1": ‚Äπ‚ä§ = ‚ùôw‚á©Œ±‚Ä∫
1559proof -
1560  AOT_have true_den: ‚Äπ‚ä§‚Üì‚Ä∫ using "A-descriptions" "rule-id-df:2:b[zero]" "the-true:1" "vdash-properties:10" by fast
1561  AOT_obtain x where x_def: ‚Äπx = ‚ä§‚Ä∫
1562    by (metis "instantiation" "rule=I:1" "existential:1" id_sym true_den)
1563  AOT_have ‚ÄπSituation(‚ä§)‚Ä∫
1564    using "T-T-value:1" "T-sit"[unvarify x, OF true_den, THEN "‚ÜíE"] by blast
1565  AOT_hence x_sit: ‚ÄπSituation(x)‚Ä∫
1566    using "rule=E"[rotated, OF x_def[symmetric]] by blast
1567
1568  AOT_have w_alpha_def: ‚Äπ‚ùôw‚á©Œ± = ‚ùôŒπw Actual(w)‚Ä∫
1569    by (simp add: "pre-walpha" "rule-id-df:1[zero]" "w-alpha")
1570  AOT_hence w_alpha_den: ‚Äπ‚ùôw‚á©Œ±‚Üì‚Ä∫
1571    using "pre-walpha" "rule-id-df:2:b[zero]" "w-alpha" by blast
1572  AOT_obtain y where y_def: ‚Äπy = ‚ùôw‚á©Œ±‚Ä∫
1573    by (metis "instantiation" "existential:1" id_sym w_alpha_def "pre-walpha")
1574  AOT_have ‚ÄπPossibleWorld(‚ùôw‚á©Œ±) & Actual(‚ùôw‚á©Œ±)‚Ä∫
1575    using "y-in:2"[unvarify z, OF w_alpha_den, THEN "‚ÜíE", OF w_alpha_def].
1576  AOT_hence y_prop: ‚ÄπPossibleWorld(y) & Actual(y)‚Ä∫
1577    using "rule=E"[rotated, OF y_def[symmetric]] by fast
1578  AOT_hence y_sit: ‚ÄπSituation(y)‚Ä∫
1579    by (meson "‚â°‚á©d‚á©fE" "&E"(1) pos "world-pos"[unconstrain w, THEN "‚ÜíE"])
1580
1581  AOT_have ‚Äπx = y‚Ä∫
1582  proof(safe intro!: "sit-identity"[unconstrain s, unconstrain s', THEN "‚ÜíE", THEN "‚ÜíE", OF y_sit, OF x_sit, THEN "‚â°E"(2)] GEN "‚â°I" "‚ÜíI")
1583    fix p
1584    AOT_assume ‚Äπx ‚ä® p‚Ä∫
1585    AOT_hence ‚Äπx[Œªy p]‚Ä∫ by (metis "‚â°‚á©d‚á©fE" "&E"(2) "prop-enc" "true-in-s")
1586    AOT_hence ‚Äπ‚ä§[Œªy p]‚Ä∫
1587      using "rule=E"[rotated, OF x_def] by fast
1588    AOT_hence ‚Äπ‚ä§‚ùôŒ£p‚Ä∫ 
1589      by (metis "‚â°‚á©d‚á©fI" "&I" "prop-enc" true_den)
1590    AOT_hence p: ‚Äπp‚Ä∫ using "q-True:3" by (metis "‚â°E"(2)) 
1591    AOT_show ‚Äπy ‚ä® p‚Ä∫
1592    proof(rule "raa-cor:1")
1593      AOT_assume ‚Äπ¬¨y ‚ä® p‚Ä∫
1594      AOT_hence ‚Äπy ‚ä® ¬¨p‚Ä∫
1595        by (metis "coherent:1"[unconstrain w, THEN "‚ÜíE"] "&E"(1) "‚â°E"(2) y_prop) 
1596      AOT_hence ‚Äπ¬¨p‚Ä∫
1597        using actual[THEN "‚â°‚á©d‚á©fE", THEN "&E"(2), THEN "‚àÄE"(1)[rotated, OF "log-prop-prop:2"], THEN "‚ÜíE", OF y_prop[THEN "&E"(2)]] by blast
1598      AOT_thus ‚Äπp & ¬¨p‚Ä∫ using p "&I" by blast
1599    qed
1600  next
1601    fix p
1602    AOT_assume ‚Äπy ‚ä® p‚Ä∫
1603    AOT_hence ‚Äπp‚Ä∫
1604      using actual[THEN "‚â°‚á©d‚á©fE", THEN "&E"(2), THEN "‚àÄE"(2), THEN "‚ÜíE", OF y_prop[THEN "&E"(2)]] by blast
1605    AOT_hence ‚Äπ‚ä§‚ùôŒ£p‚Ä∫ by (metis "‚â°E"(1) "q-True:3")
1606    AOT_hence ‚Äπx‚ùôŒ£p‚Ä∫ using "rule=E"[rotated, OF x_def[symmetric]] by fast
1607    AOT_thus ‚Äπx ‚ä® p‚Ä∫
1608      by (metis "‚â°‚á©d‚á©fI" "&I" "true-in-s" x_sit)
1609  qed
1610  AOT_thus ‚Äπ‚ä§ = ‚ùôw‚á©Œ±‚Ä∫
1611    using "rule=E"[rotated, OF x_def] "rule=E"[rotated, OF y_def] by (metis id_sym)
1612qed

1661AOT_theorem "t-at-alpha-strict": ‚Äπ‚ùôw‚á©Œ± ‚ä® p ‚â° ‚ùôùíúp‚Ä∫

1681       using actual "‚â°Df" apply blast

1683    AOT_hence ‚Äπ‚ùôùíú‚àÄq(‚ùôw‚á©Œ± ‚ä® q ‚Üí q)‚Ä∫ by (metis "Act-Basic:2" "&E"(2) "‚â°E"(1))

1685      using "logic-actual-nec:3"[axiom_inst, THEN "‚â°E"(1)] by blast

1687    AOT_hence ‚Äπ‚ùôùíú(‚ùôw‚á©Œ± ‚ä® p) ‚Üí ‚ùôùíúp‚Ä∫ by (metis "act-cond" "vdash-properties:10")

1689  }
1690  AOT_hence 2: ‚Äπ‚ùôw‚á©Œ± ‚ä® p ‚Üí ‚ùôùíúp‚Ä∫ for p by (rule "‚ÜíI")
1691  AOT_have walpha_sit: ‚ÄπSituation(‚ùôw‚á©Œ±)‚Ä∫

1693  show ?thesis
1694  proof(safe intro!: "‚â°I" "‚ÜíI" 2)
1695    AOT_assume actp: ‚Äπ‚ùôùíúp‚Ä∫
1696    AOT_show ‚Äπ‚ùôw‚á©Œ± ‚ä® p‚Ä∫
1697    proof(rule "raa-cor:1")
1698      AOT_assume ‚Äπ¬¨‚ùôw‚á©Œ± ‚ä® p‚Ä∫
1699      AOT_hence ‚Äπ‚ùôw‚á©Œ± ‚ä® ¬¨p‚Ä∫
1700        using "alpha-world:2"[THEN max[THEN "‚â°‚á©d‚á©fE"], THEN "&E"(2), THEN "‚àÄE"(1), OF "log-prop-prop:2"]
1701        by (metis "‚à®E"(2))
1702      AOT_hence ‚Äπ‚ùôùíú¬¨p‚Ä∫
1703        using 2[unvarify p, OF "log-prop-prop:2", THEN "‚ÜíE"] by blast

1710AOT_act_theorem "not-act": ‚Äπw ‚â† ‚ùôw‚á©Œ± ‚Üí ¬¨Actual(w)‚Ä∫
